rows.label: qst100306_msg0002
rows.name:
Old friend who give Panpan tasty food,
and took care of Vacuum Brogs!
...And got parts for repair...hehe...

rows.label: qst100306_msg0003
rows.name:
Thanks to friends'...constant...support,
Panpan complete full 40 hours of flight
training!

rows.label: qst100306_msg0004
rows.name:
Panpan got license with big rubber
stamp. Now fully-fledged Nopon pilot!

rows.label: qst100306_msg0006
rows.name:
Friend want thank-you for tasty treats?
And money for parts?

rows.label: qst100306_msg0007
rows.name:
Ah, actually... Panpan not begin career
quite yet... A bit broke... Training fees...

rows.label: qst100306_msg0008
rows.name:
Oh, but this terrible! Panpan have
sudden feeling that flying skills are
fading away!

rows.label: qst100306_msg0009
rows.name:
Panpan lose skills if not make regular
flights...

rows.label: qst100306_msg0010
rows.name:
Yes, Panpan must go off flying again
right now. So, byeeeee!
